Illusion (Glamer)
Level: Brd 1, Sor/Wiz 1
Components: V
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 2 rounds
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: No

With a single spoken syllable, the caster disappears from sight with a brief puff of smoke.  For the round of casting, and the round directly after, the caster remains invisible, as by the spell invisibility, with normal restrictions on attacking and the like.